Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,莎珂 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我从格奥尔格伯爵那里听到了所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你为Headkeeper…不 为反帝派提供了帮助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲还活着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能这么相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我都不知道自己为了什么帮助他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,活着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就在帝都 现在还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,杰德 你为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有报告说你们回来了 而且不是去我那里 而是回了老家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你们会在逮捕行动中都被抓起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,结果好像还被你们知道了很多闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你…用辉光之种杀了那么多人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一半是我 但另一半呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 虽然让你们在监狱里来个母女重逢也挺感人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但人质有一个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊 我不是一直都乖乖听你们的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,已经用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还是动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…莎珂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事? 这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,咦? 怎么了? 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…那是灾祸之光?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,帝都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是假货?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点 走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,站得起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走 大家有秩序地转移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 接下来该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,「喔」你个头啊 莱奥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,卡雅 露 哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不在? 他们去哪儿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,已经去避难了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事啦 他肯定还活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那小子顽强得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊 肯定没事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们自己得先没事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可别真的死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样子…是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,灾祸之光…落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…最后实验的…集大成…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其答案…和…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和光…融合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,融合?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你也…你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,融合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要先干什么啊? 这个情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是预言的灾难吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来还以为应该更晚一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办? 该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要去帝城吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别说傻话了 那不是自杀吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在已经管不了什么反帝派了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也是哦 那要去据点吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了 想想格奥尔格伯爵说的那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,「摇篮」开始启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没时间了 城市会被封锁的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…以努麦尔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…以努麦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这里吧 外面出事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…发生了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麦尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧? 能…认得出我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,莱奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迪欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看这情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是没法交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,从古泰尔到帝都这么远都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到底严重到什么地步? 完全想象不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你们了 一定要没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 住手啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是莱奥卡迪欧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,莱奥?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对 是莱奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不当人了吗 以努麦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我清醒点 以努麦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,送货员以努麦尔·格劳纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你认不出我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,认不…认…认不出…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是为什么要回帝都的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不是下定了某种决心回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,决心?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别胡闹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你个通缉犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,通缉…通缉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你要给我找多少麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,才满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还想连我也杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,变异?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是觉醒者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想…想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希赛尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 认得出我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,莱奥卡迪欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,终于恢复清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,站得起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,答应…给浮士德的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,应该有治疗雷火病的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会交给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…你会有这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是希赛尔要我交给你的 结果我给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为发生太多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这东西算是救了我一命 就原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,摇篮会将帝都封锁 到时候你就出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…有什么要对你妹妹希赛尔说的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥的事…很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,居然比我先到啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔…你居然还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是我要说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麦尔和本呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,阿诺 现在能走了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也没时间沮丧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麦尔 你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在就回句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麦尔 该醒醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能从这地下通道出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,难道地底下住着这种东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,差点就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害啊…从来没看到过这么大规模的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能把整个城市都封锁起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样根本联系不上同伴们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 你今后怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去找康拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该和我弟弟妹妹…还有希赛尔一起去避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去一趟新都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 大叔我陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,借的装备也得还回去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我觉得那已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别跟过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(918,995)}Wahrheit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 迎接瓦尔海特帝国新的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是惨啊 那道光落下才两周就乱成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,无政府状态 无法地带 完全为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不过毕竟比那里面要好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿诺德他们还活着吗? 搞不好变成怪物了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怜 帝国军也失去了指挥系统 分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,传说还有些不法之徒 打着帝国兵的名号当强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道康拉德和莱奥还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,保护好…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}陛下…皇后…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子…求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 救救她吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是皇族的纹章?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,萝洁玛丽…皇帝陛下的女儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你…照顾好她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,「又」是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是一个招来麻烦事的天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
